{"id":1933087,"date":"2024-06-22T16:00:00","date_gmt":"2024-06-22T10:30:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=1933087"},"modified":"2024-12-11T11:13:03","modified_gmt":"2024-12-11T05:43:03","slug":"how-journalism-degree-help-you-stay-future-ready","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/how-journalism-degree-help-you-stay-future-ready","title":{"rendered":"How a degree in journalism would benefit in a fast-changing media scenario"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The media landscape is ever-evolving and rapidly changing, thanks to the multifarious technological advancements, evolving industry standards, and changing consumer behavioral trends. The advent and growth of social media platforms, coupled with the hogging of the digital space by Artificial Intelligence and Data Analytics, has helped reshape the media scenario completely. In this ever-changing landscape, the one thing that continues to hold strong ground is a degree in Journalism. A professional qualification helps keep in tune with the skills required for continual advancement in the field and also allows for quick adaptability to the changing domain. This blog highlights the top benefits of getting a journalism degree online.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also like: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/role-of-podcasts-in-modern-journalism-education\">Role of Podcasts in modern journalism education<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-understanding-the-modern-media-landscape\"><strong>Understanding the Modern Media Landscape<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Let us take a minute to understand how exactly the modern media landscape is changing by the day:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Technological Advancements: <\/strong>Technology has transformed media consumption and production considerably. There has been a steady rise in digital media, social platforms, and multimedia storytelling, marking a shift from traditional print and broadcast media to online platforms.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Changing Audience Preferences: <\/strong>The audience is also gradually shifting toward personalized and interactive content. Streaming services like Netflix and YouTube, on-demand audio podcasts, and interactive social media platforms have enabled real-time interactions between content creators and their respective target audiences.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/career-in-journalism-how-an-online-ma-is-an-ideal-option\">Career in Journalism: How an online MA is an ideal option<\/a>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-core-skills-developed-through-a-journalism-degree\"><strong>Core Skills Developed through a Journalism Degree:<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Considering the ever-changing media landscape, a journalism degree tends to stay constant in terms of equipping students with a wide array of core skills that prepare them for varied roles in the fields of public relations, communications, digital media, and marketing.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Given below is a list of some of the key skills that can help improve your employability for <strong>career opportunities after a Journalism degree:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Research and Analytical Skills:<\/strong> Journalism programs teach students to conduct thorough research, analyze data, and verify information, which are critical in producing accurate and credible news. Students learn the key fundamentals of research, identify credible information sources, and conduct interviews to gather information.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Writing and Communication:<\/strong> Strong writing and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/career-in-journalism-how-an-online-ma-is-an-ideal-option\">communication skills<\/a>, such as storytelling techniques that help engage diverse audiences, are equally important and taught in journalism courses. The program imparts learning in linguistic precision and clear articulation, professionalism and credibility, and cultural sensitivity and inclusivity.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-adaptability-and-versatility\"><strong>Adaptability and Versatility<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>These are the two other core <strong>skills developed through a journalism degree<\/strong>. Here\u2019s what the program imparts:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Multimedia proficiency:<\/strong> Students of journalism learn to create content over varied media formats and channels. A fine blend of theory and practice helps students gain the desired experience in the domain.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Adaptability to change:<\/strong> Students are equipped with adaptability skills to new tools and technologies in the media industry, which is reflected in the evolving curriculum, and the desire to make students technically proficient in video editing software such as Adobe Premiere Pro, CMS WordPress, and Google Analytics evaluation platforms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the article on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/impact-of-ai-in-media\">impact of AI in the media industry<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ethics-and-credibility-nbsp-nbsp\"><strong>Ethics and Credibility<\/strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with proficiency in various other skills, students of online journalism degrees are taught the valued skills of ethics, trust, and integrity:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Journalistic ethics:<\/strong> The special focus is on covering topics like media ethics, accuracy, honesty, objectivity in reporting, transparency, legal compliance, and ethical practice.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Building trust:<\/strong> A strong ethical foundation can help journalists build trust with their audience, which is crucial in an era of misinformation. The students\u2019 commitment to checking factual accuracy, ensuring source credibility, fair and unbiased reporting, and accountability to their target audience keeps them grounded and ethical in day-to-day activities.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/evolution-of-journalism-in-the-digital-era\">Evolution of Journalism in the Digital Era<\/a>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-career-opportunities-in-the-evolving-media-industry\"><strong>Career Opportunities in the Evolving Media Industry<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We took a closer look at the <strong>modern media landscape and the journalism degree<\/strong>\u2019s contribution to its ever-evolving structure. Let us now review some of the top career prospects in this booming sector:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Traditional roles:<\/strong> Listed below are some of the conventional roles found in this industry:<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Job role<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Average annual salary (approx)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Broadcaster<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.salaryexpert.com\/salary\/job\/broadcast-journalist\/india\">INR 16,64,410 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Editor<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.glassdoor.co.in\/Career\/editor-career_KO0,6.htm\">INR 6.15 lakh per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Reporter&nbsp;<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/worldsalaries.com\/average-news-reporter-salary-in-india\/\">INR 4,20,800 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Emerging roles:<\/strong> As the above roles continue to evolve to keep pace with the changing media landscape, some of the new and emerging career paths are tabulated below:<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Job role<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Average annual salary (approx)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Digital Content Creator<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/digital-content-creator-salary\">INR 4 lakh per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Social Media Manager<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/in.talent.com\/salary?job=social+media+manager\">INR 4,50,000 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Data Journalist&nbsp;<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.glassdoor.co.in\/Salaries\/data-journalist-salary-SRCH_KO0,15.htm#:~:text=Data%20Journalist%20Salaries%20in%20India&amp;text=The%20national%20average%20salary%20for,Glassdoor%20by%20Data%20journalist%20employees.\">INR 8,25,000 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-networking-and-professional-growth\"><strong>Networking and Professional Growth<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Like any other industry, it is important to network for professional growth and career development. Making the right industry connections and continual learning to upskill yourself is key to keeping pace with the rapidly evolving media industry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Online journalism programs provide ample opportunities for networking via internships, workshops, and alumni networks. In addition to this, the importance of lifelong learning and professional development in staying relevant in the fast-changing media landscape must be underlined here. This helps adapt to technological advancements in the domain and helps stay relevant to industry trends. Upskilling also enables gaining specialization in a specific domain area which in turn facilitates career advancement.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read more about the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/7-advantages-of-mobile-journalism-mojo\">7 advantages of mobile journalism &#8211; MoJo<\/a>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-take-your-career-forward-with-online-manipal\"><strong>Take your career forward with Online Manipal<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to take the first step in the rewarding media industry? An online MA in Journalism and Mass Communication (JMC) from Manipal University Jaipur can help you take your career forward in the domain.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The two-year program is designed to create leaders in the field of journalism and mass communication by equipping skills that provide learners with hands-on experience in scriptwriting, screenwriting, photography, mobile editing software, and writing for new media.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Master of Arts degree can be pursued in 100% online mode on the Online Manipal platform without disturbing your continuing work commitments and other engagements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-conclusion\"><strong>Conclusion<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This blog stresses how a degree in journalism can help students keep pace with the fast-changing and ever-evolving media landscape in India. Additionally, pursuing the degree online is equally beneficial in imparting the required skills and enabling students to study and work alongside others.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re looking for a viable and rewarding career option in today&#8217;s fast-paced media world, an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-arts-in-journalism-mass-communication\">online MA-JMC<\/a> from Manipal University Jaipur can be the perfect answer. The degree lends a strong foundation in establishing research and investigative skills, enabling students to unearth and factually report complex stories that inform and influence public opinion and policy.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The program also facilitates a deeper understanding of media laws and ethics, ensuring that students always uphold integrity and accountability in their work. It also provides hands-on experience with the latest digital tools and multimedia, preparing students for excellence in roles that require technical proficiency.&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The media landscape is ever-evolving and rapidly changing, thanks to the multifarious technological advancements, evolving industry standards, and changing consumer behavioral trends. The advent and growth of social media platforms, coupled with the hogging of the digital space by Artificial Intelligence and Data Analytics, has helped reshape the media scenario completely. In this ever-changing landscape, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":19,"featured_media":1933183,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[25],"tags":[19],"class_list":["post-1933087","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-media-journalism","tag-online-degree"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>How a degree in journalism would benefit in a fast-changing media scenario - Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Learn how an online degree in journalism holds relevance and significance in a rapid and ever-changing media landscape.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1933087\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How a degree in journalism would benefit in a fast-changing media scenario - Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Learn how an online degree in journalism holds relevance and significance in a rapid and ever-changin