 the recent developments in online education. We enable readers to gain insights into the trending online degrees, their scope &amp; benefits, and help them make informed decisions that will result in career advancement and transitions.\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/author\\\/online-manipal-editorial-team\"}]}<\/script>\n<!-- \/ Yoast SEO plugin. -->","yoast_head_json":{"title":"How a degree in journalism would benefit in a fast-changing media scenario - Online Manipal","description":"Learn how an online degree in journalism holds relevance and significance in a rapid and ever-changing media landscape.","robots":{"index":"index","follow":"follow","max-snippet":"max-snippet:-1","max-image-preview":"max-image-preview:large","max-video-preview":"max-video-preview:-1"},"canonical":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1933087","og_locale":"en_GB","og_type":"article","og_title":"How a degree in journalism would benefit in a fast-changing media scenario - Online Manipal","og_description":"Learn how an online degree in journalism holds relevance and significance in a rapid and ever-changing media landscape.","og_url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/how-journalism-degree-help-you-stay-future-ready","og_site_name":"Online Manipal","article_publisher":"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal","article_published_time":"2024-06-22T10:30:00+00:00","article_modified_time":"2024-12-11T05:43:03+00:00","og_image":[{"width":706,"height":395,"url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Thumbnails-Online-learning-7.jpg","type":"image\/jpeg"}],"author":"Editorial Team","twitter_card":"summary_large_image","twitter_misc":{"Written by":"Editorial Team","Estimated reading time":"6 minutes"},"schema":{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/how-journalism-degree-help-you-stay-future-ready","url":"